      "about.label": "About INTEC",
      "about.missionTitle": "Mission &amp; Vision",
      "about.missionIntro":
        "We work towards a society where everyone can fully participate in the digital world. Regardless of background, age, gender or education we focus on talent and lower the barriers to quality jobs.",
      "about.missionDetail":
        "Our programmes combine technical expertise with language coaching, soft skills and sustainable follow-up. We connect job seekers, employers and society at large with inclusion and future skills as our compass.",
      "about.hero.title": "Mission & Vision",
      "about.hero.lead":
        "We build a society where everyone can be part of the digital world. Talent is central regardless of background or age. We lower barriers to sustainable jobs and strengthen digital skills at every step.",
      "about.hero.chip1": "Inclusive programmes",
      "about.hero.chip2": "Digital and future-proof",
      "about.hero.chip3": "Language coaching & support",
      "about.hero.primary": "Explore programmes",
      "about.hero.secondary": "Schedule an introduction",
      "about.values.label": "Impact",
      "about.values.title": "What drives us every day",
      "about.values.lead":
        "Each programme and track is built on the same foundations: people-focused, sustainable and digital. Together with our partners we help talent grow and make organisations future-ready.",
      "about.values.card1Title": "Access for everyone",
      "about.values.card1Body":
        "From language support to digicoaches: we ensure every talent can join and progress.",
      "about.values.card2Title": "Strong partnerships",
      "about.values.card2Body":
        "We work with companies, public services and non-profits to create impact in Brussels and Flanders.",
      "about.values.card3Title": "Innovation with people",
      "about.values.card3Body":
        "Technology is not a goal by itself: we combine digital know-how with soft skills and coaching.",
      "about.values.card4Title": "Sustainable careers",
      "about.values.card4Body":
        "We support alumni up to one year after graduation and invest in long-term employment.",
      "about.valuesTitle": "Our values",
      "about.values.quality": "Quality and continuous improvement in programmes and coaching.",
      "about.values.respect": "Respect, openness and transparency in every collaboration.",
      "about.values.teamwork": "Teamwork and a growth mindset across disciplines.",
      "about.values.innovation": "Innovation with attention for people and society.",
      "about.buttons.report": "Annual report",
      "about.buttons.team": "Meet the team",
      "about.workTitle": "Working at INTEC Brussels?",
      "about.workIntro":
        "Join a diverse and committed team that empowers people through training and coaching. We collaborate across disciplines and invest in equal opportunities and lifelong learning.",
      "about.workDetail":
        "Trainers, coaches, digicoaches and support profiles share knowledge, design learning paths and guide participants towards sustainable employment.",
      "about.workCta": "See vacancies",
      "about.experienceTitle": "Experience since 2001",
      "about.experienceIntro":
        "Over twenty years ago we started as a VDAB training partner. Today we support job seekers, starters and professionals into digital and technical careers.",
      "about.experienceDetail":
        "Our programmes balance hard skills, soft skills and long-term employment. Alumni find their place in consultancy, healthcare, public services and startups. We invest in lasting partnerships so talent keeps growing.",
      "about.journey.label": "Our approach",
      "about.journey.title": "From talent to sustainable employment",
      "about.journey.step1Title": "1. Intake & selection",
      "about.journey.step1Body":
        "We begin with info sessions, assessments and language checks to make sure each participant joins the right track.",
      "about.journey.step2Title": "2. Learning & coaching",
      "about.journey.step2Body":
